ty-page-layout\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mobile-toc-button\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L30\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mobile-toc-trigger\\\",\\\"targetSelector\\\":\\\".table-of-contents\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-list-ul\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Contents\\\"}]]}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"id\\\":\\\"city-hero\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"city-hero-section \\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"section-shell city-hero-shell\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"city-hero-copy\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-breadcrumbs\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Home\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-chevron-right\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-chevron-right\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Columbus\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-eyebrow\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Campus-friendly indoor runs\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h1\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Indoor dog park in Columbus, Ohio\\\"}],\\\"$undefined\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"College-town schedules crave memberships and combined daycare/boarding packages so students, med staff, and tech workers can keep a steady indoor routine.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"city-rich-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Columbus has developed a unique indoor dog park culture that caters to its massive student population at Ohio State and a growing workforce of medical professionals. The city’s volatile weather, featuring humid summers and gray winters, makes climate-controlled play an essential part of local pet ownership. In districts like the Short North, facilities have pioneered a \\\\\\\"study-and-play\\\\\\\" model, blending traditional indoor runs with coworking pods and high-speed Wi-Fi. This concept is incredibly popular among the city’s 60,000+ college students, who use these spaces as a base of operations while their pets burn energy under staff supervision. While \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://columbusrecparks.com\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Columbus Recreation and Parks\\\"}],null,\\\" offers excellent public grounds, the private indoor clubs distinguish themselves with premium amenities like lockers, barista service, and even dorm-friendly shuttle services that integrate into an active lifestyle.\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"The operational focus in Columbus is heavily influenced by the academic calendar and the needs of shift workers. Professional membership structures are often flexible, featuring semester-based plans that align with OSU’s schedule, typically costing between $120 and $180 per term. Daily drop-ins are available for approximately $16 to $20, providing a convenient option for an occasional break from the elements. Safety and hygiene are maintained through rigorous standards, including antimicrobial turf and mandatory temperament checks for all new participants. Many facilities also offer \\\\\\\"sniffari\\\\\\\" sessions and scent-work labs for mental enrichment. Owners can find more detailed guidance on coordinating these sessions with their schedules in our \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"#planning-essentials\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"planning essentials\\\"}],null,\\\" guide. By combining education-friendly environments with a focus on local demographics, Columbus’s indoor dog parks have established themselves as vital neighborhood anchors year-round.\\\"]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta-row\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L30\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta primary\\\",\\\"targetId\\\":\\\"park-directory\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-list-check\\\"}],\\\"Browse directory\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L30\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-cta ghost\\\",\\\"targetId\\\":\\\"map-and-neighborhoods\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$L31\\\",\\\"Open map\\\"]}],\\\"$L32\\\"]}],\\\"$L33\\\"]}],\\\"$L34\\\"]}]}],\\\"$L35\\\",\\\"$L36\\\",\\\"$L37\\\",\\\"$L38\\\",\\\"$L39\\\",\\\"$L3a\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$L3b\\\",\\\"$L3c\\\",\\\"$L3d\\\",\\\"$L3e\\\",\\\"$L3f\\\"]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"2b:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"footer\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-new\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-container\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-grid\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-column\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h4\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-heading\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"IndoorDogPark\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ul\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-links\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/about\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"About us\\\"}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/partners\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Partners\\\"}]}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-column\\\",\\\